-//   - weather: map (required) - Current weather conditions
-//   - createdAt: timestamp (optional) - When the user was created
-//
-// Collection: transfers
-// Document ID: {transferId} (Auto-generated)
-// Fields:
-//   - from: string (required) - Sender UID
-//   - to: string (required) - Receiver UID
